  "serviceType": "Stove and Range Repair",
  "name": "Stove & Range Repair, Same Day Appliance Repair",
  "description": "Same-day stove and range repair across Los Angeles, Orange, Ventura, San Bernardino, and Riverside counties. Gas, electric, induction, dual-fuel, luxury and standard brands.",
