        <ul>
          <li>A $400 repair on a $6,000 Wolf range is 6.7% of replacement cost</li>
          <li>These ranges are built to last 20+ years with proper service</li>
          <li>Parts availability is excellent, specialty distributors stock them</li>
          <li>Resale value of a working luxury range is significant</li>
          <li>Repair is almost always the right call at any reasonable repair cost</li>
