          <li>Under 50% of replacement cost → repair makes sense</li>
          <li>Control board replacement on a $700 range: borderline, we'll say so</li>
          <li>Igniter, element, infinite switch → almost always worth repairing</li>
          <li>10+ year old unit with control board failure → replacement often better</li>
          <li>We give you the repair cost before you decide, no pressure either way</li>
